<div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide">
  <div class="carousel-indicators">
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
    <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
  </div>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <%= image_tag("img1.png") %>
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>Organized Workflows</h5>
        <p>Say goodbye to cluttered notes and chaotic drafts with MyManuscript. Our intuitive organization tools make it easy to keep your work organized and your writing process streamlined.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <%= image_tag("img2.png") %>
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5>Convenient Writing</h5>
        <p>Write your next manuscript with ease and convenience using MyManuscript. Our streamlined platform allows you to focus on your writing without distractions.
</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <%= image_tag("img3.png") %>
      <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
        <h5> Secure Storage</h5>
        <p>Keep your writing safe and secure with MyManuscript. Our state-of-the-art security measures ensure that your work is protected and only accessible to you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
  </button>
  <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
  </button>
</div>